Package com.google.api.client.googleapis.auth

Utilities for Google's authentication methods as described in Getting Started with Account Authorization .

This package depends on thetheses packages:

  • com.google.api.client.http
    • and
  • com.google.api.client.util packages.

Warning: this package is experimental, and its content may be changed in incompatible ways or possibly entirely removed in a future version of the library
